        <title>Rising From the Ashes Oral Histories</title>
    </titleInfo>
    <abstract>Rising from the Ashes documents the effects of the 2016 Chimney Tops 2 wildfires, one of the largest natural disasters in Tennessee history. It shares approximately 140 interviews with individuals impacted by the wildfires.</abstract>
